== standard option state:
errtrace-on
functrace-on
braceexpand-on
hashall-on
keyword-on
== brace expansion follows its option:
<{a,b}>
<c>
<d>
== vi and emacs can both be off:
vi-off
emacs-off
== command substitution isolates option state:
notify         	off
== runtime noexec stops later commands:
noexec-clean
nested-noexec-clean
== function option changes survive defining-mood state:
function-option-persisted
strict-markers-persisted
== command strings publish c in dollar dash:
command-string
== interactive state is independent of hashall:
interactive
== SHELLOPTS uses the shared option state:
braceexpand-listed
hashall-listed
== physical mode resolves a symlinked directory:
physical=yes
physical-cdpath=yes
physical-dotdot=yes
